1. *Prošlost* je zauvek nestala. (The past is gone forever.)
2. On je zaboravio svoju *prošlost*. (He forgot his past.)
3. *Prošlost* nas čini onim što smo danas. (The past makes us who we are today.)
4. Nastojimo da naučimo iz naše *prošlosti*. (We try to learn from our past.)
5. *Prošlost* je postavila temelje za budućnost. (The past has laid the foundation for the future.)